OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1772301852
OL,3,CExtra police over weekend to 'deter
OL,4,Ccrime' after Sheffield school brawl
OL,6,FExtra officers will remain in the Page
OL,7,FHall area of Sheffield this weekend
OL,8,Fafter a brawl at a Sheffield school.
OL,10,FSouth Yorkshire Police were called to
OL,11,FFir Vale Academy in the city on
OL,12,FThursday after a fight broke out
OL,13,Famongst students, leaving a number of
OL,14,Fstaff and pupils hurt.
OL,16,FThe force said both staff and pupils
OL,17,Fwere hurt.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/5
