OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1772301852
OL,3,CExtra police over weekend to 'deter
OL,4,Ccrime' after Sheffield school brawl
OL,6,FA letter issued to parents by the
OL,7,Facademy's principal claimed the fight
OL,8,Fhad been the result of "recent
OL,9,Fcommunity tensions", and that they
OL,10,Fwould ensure those responsible would
OL,11,Fbe dealt with.
OL,13,FPrincipal Danny Bullock added that the
OL,14,Fschool was "a place of respect,
OL,15,Flearning and stability" and was "not
OL,16,Fthe appropriate forum" for those
OL,17,Ftensions to be addressed.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
