CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1772301852
OL,3,CExtra police over weekend to 'deter
OL,4,Ccrime' after Sheffield school brawl
OL,6,FA staff member was reportedly
OL,7,Fhospitalised following the fracas,
OL,8,Fthough police confirmed on Friday that
OL,9,Fnobody was seriously injured.
OL,11,FAn investigation is now underway.
OL,13,FSouth Yorkshire Police said it would
OL,14,Fbe stepping up patrols in the area to
OL,15,Freassure concerned locals.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
