OL,3,CExtra police over weekend to 'deter
OL,4,Ccrime' after Sheffield school brawl
OL,6,FSuperintendent Paul Ferguson said: "We
OL,7,Fknow that this incident has caused
OL,8,Fsome concern in the community ` our
OL,9,Fofficers who are in the area have
OL,10,Freported the streets being quieter
OL,11,Fthan usual.
OL,13,F"Our investigation is ongoing and,
OL,14,Fwith both pupils and staff being hurt,
OL,15,Fwe are committed to working with the
OL,16,Fschool and the Youth Justice Service
OL,17,Fto ensure appropriate action is taken
OL,18,Fagainst those who encourage or
OL,19,Fparticipate in disorder."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/5
